<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 06:19:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>华为威胁迫在眉睫，苹果新 iPhone 中的人工智能差距令中国用户失望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apples-ai-gap-new-iphones-disappoints-china-users-huawei-threat-looms-2024-09-10/</link><description>苹果公司周二推出的新款 iPhone 因其缺乏人工智能功能而在中国遭到嘲笑，这对这家美国巨头来说是一个挑战，因为它在全球最大的智能手机市场上与华为技术公司 (HWT.UL) 日益激烈的竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 05:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apples-ai-gap-new-iphones-disappoints-china-users-huawei-threat-looms-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>万宝盛华调查显示第四季度全球招聘意向保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-hiring-intentions-hold-steady-q4-manpowergroup-survey-shows-2024-09-10/</link><description>万宝盛华集团的就业前景调查显示，尽管未来季度的前景弱于 2023 年最后一个季度，但企业的全球招聘意向预计将在 2024 年第四季度保持稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 05:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-hiring-intentions-hold-steady-q4-manpowergroup-survey-shows-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车供应商和电动汽车制造商涌入德国主要贸易展览会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-auto-suppliers-ev-makers-flood-major-trade-fair-germany-2024-09-10/</link><description>近 900 家中国汽车供应商和少数电动汽车制造商正在法兰克福的一个贸易展览会上展示他们的产品，因为中国汽车行业不顾迫在眉睫的贸易壁垒，扩大其全球足迹并应对国内盈利能力受到侵蚀的局面。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 05:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-auto-suppliers-ev-makers-flood-major-trade-fair-germany-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国经济低迷掩盖了华尔街主导的反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-10/</link><description>Rae Wee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 04:35:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口超预期，进口受内需低迷影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-top-forecasts-imports-disappoint-amid-depressed-domestic-demand-2024-09-10/</link><description>8月份，中国出口增速创近1-1/2年来最快，这表明制造商正在赶在越来越多贸易伙伴预计加征关税之前抢下订单，而由于内需疲弱，进口未达预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 03:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-top-forecasts-imports-disappoint-amid-depressed-domestic-demand-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中美军方高层首次视频通话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-chinese-military-officials-hold-first-video-call-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国当局表示，美国和中国周二首次举行战区级指挥官会谈，两国希望稳定军事关系并防止军事误解。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 03:26:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-chinese-military-officials-hold-first-video-call-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>华为推出三折智能手机，加剧与苹果在中国的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-teases-tri-fold-smartphone-raising-competition-with-apple-china-2024-09-10/</link><description>中国华为技术有限公司 (HWT.UL) 周二推出了一款三向可折叠手机，旨在凭借在中国广受欢迎的新外形，扩大其在全球最大智能手机市场对苹果的领先地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 02:03:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-teases-tri-fold-smartphone-raising-competition-with-apple-china-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国阻碍亚洲股市反弹；美国数据，美联储会议即将召开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-10/</link><description>亚洲股市周二小幅走高，但由于对中国经济步履蹒跚的担忧打压了市场情绪，华尔街股市难以维持乐观涨势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 01:55:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>美元稳定，日元在美国通胀数据公布前波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-with-caution-ahead-us-inflation-test-2024-09-10/</link><description>美元周二持稳，日元在谨慎交易中小幅脱离一个月高点，因投资者为美国通胀数据做好准备，并重新评估美联储下周大​​幅降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 01:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-with-caution-ahead-us-inflation-test-2024-09-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国限制与中国药明康德、华大基因开展业务的法案众议院通过</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bill-restrict-business-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-passes-house-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国众议院周一通过了一项法案，旨在以国家安全为由限制与中国药明康德、华大基因和其他几家生物技术公司的业务往来。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 23:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bill-restrict-business-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-passes-house-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>“中国周”即将到来，美国众议院投票禁止新的大疆无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-votes-bar-new-drones-chinese-manufacturer-dji-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国众议院周一投票禁止中国无人机制造商大疆创新的新无人机在美国运营，这是立法者本周考虑的一系列针对中国的措施之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 20:53:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-house-votes-bar-new-drones-chinese-manufacturer-dji-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国提议要求先进人工智能、云提供商报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-requiring-reporting-advanced-ai-cloud-providers-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国商务部周一表示，提议要求先进人工智能开发商和云计算提供商提供详细的报告要求，以确保技术安全并能够抵御网络攻击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-requiring-reporting-advanced-ai-cloud-providers-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>在苹果 iPhone 16 发布之前，华为三折手机预订量已达 300 万部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-racks-up-3-mln-pre-orders-tri-fold-phone-before-apples-iphone-16-reveal-2024-09-09/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为的网站周一显示，其三折叠智能手机的预订量已超过 300 万部，而就在苹果推出新一代 iPhone 的几个小时前。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-racks-up-3-mln-pre-orders-tri-fold-phone-before-apples-iphone-16-reveal-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平寻求与挪威在绿色能源领域开展“友好”合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-seeks-friendly-cooperation-with-norway-green-energy-evs-2024-09-09/</link><description>国家主席习近平周一在北京对来访的挪威首相斯托雷表示，中国愿与挪威共同推动包括绿色能源在内的“友好”合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-seeks-friendly-cooperation-with-norway-green-energy-evs-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>苹果 iPhone 16 发布会展示 AI 肌肉、新款手表和 AirPods</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apples-iphone-16-will-put-ai-features-focus-2024-09-09/</link><description>苹果周一推出了人们期待已久的人工智能增强版 iPhone 16，以及具有助听功能的 AirPods，并已提交美国监管机构审查，并更新了手表。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/apples-iphone-16-will-put-ai-features-focus-2024-09-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>